Sonterra Apartments<br>
5050 Tamarus Street, Las Vegas, NV 89119<br>
<br>
<br>
Spacious 1BR/1BA Apartment - 680 sqft<br>
<br>
Monthly Rent $1085.00<br>
This rental fee includes Utilities such as Water, Sewer and Trash.<br>
<br>
*Please note, Electricity with Nevada Energy is not included in the rental fee listed above.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Rental Criteria:<br>
<br>
No Evictions or Rental Collections<br>
<br>
No Misdemeanors or Felonies<br>
<br>
No Child support collections exceeding $20,000.00<br>
<br>
Proof of Steady Monthly Income - Must add up to DOUBLE the Rent Amount<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Ready to apply? Heres what you should bring:<br>
<br>
Driver License/ Identification Card (current &amp; Government-issued)<br>
<br>
Proof of Social Security Number or ITIN<br>
<br>
Contact information for prior landlords<br>
<br>
2-4 Recent Pay stubs/ Verifiable Proof of Income<br>
<br>
<br>
The rental application can be located at www.SonterraLV.com<br>
*$55.00 Nonrefundable Application Fee required for each applicant over 18 years old.<br>
<br>
<br>
Upon approval, Approved applicants have 48 hours max to submit Holding Fee payment of $250.00. Please keep in mind, this holding fee can hold the unit for no longer than 2 weeks max. Approved applicants must complete the move in process within 2 weeks from the date of application approval.<br>
*This $250.00 Holding fee will also be deducted from the security deposit amount upon move in.<br>
<br>
Security Deposit upon approval is as followed:<br>
$500.00<br>
$750.00<br>
$1000.00<br>
-The security deposit amount varies based upon verifiable information submitted with the rental application. Once the application is submitted, please allow up to 5 days max before expecting a status update regarding application status.<br>
<br>
Westland Real Estate Group is a family-owned company that features 30 multi-family communities throughout Las Vegas. With over 10,000 units in the area, we offer everything from studios to three-bedroom townhomes, with a variety of in-demand amenities. Enjoy stress-free living in our well-maintained communities with clean grounds and professional staff. At Westland, you’ve found a place where you can invest in your future
